{"word":"G3706 - ὅρασις - hórasis - hor'-as-is - Sight","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὅρασις</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hórasis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hor'-as-is"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Sight"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல் - தரிசனம், பார்வை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. the act of seeing"},{"paragraph":"2. appearance, visible form"},{"paragraph":"3. a vision"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3708 - ὁράω - horáō - hor-ah'-o/3708\">G3708</a>; the act of <i>gazing</i>, that is, (external) an <i>aspect</i> or (internal) an inspired <i>appearance:</i> - sight, vision."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2300 - θεάομαι - theáomai - theh-ah'-om-ahee/2300\">G2300</a>, <a href=\"#/G2334 - θεωρέω - theōréō - theh-o-reh'-o/2334\">G2334</a>, <a href=\"#/G2529 - καθοράω - kathoráō - kath-or-ah'-o/2529\">G2529</a>, <a href=\"#/G3705 - ὅραμα - hórama - hor'-am-ah/3705\">G3705</a>, <a href=\"#/G3706 - ὅρασις - hórasis - hor'-as-is/3706\">G3706</a>, <a href=\"#/G3707 - ὁρατός - horatós - hor-at-os'/3707\">G3707</a>, <a href=\"#/G3708 - ὁράω - horáō - hor-ah'-o/3708\">G3708</a>, <a href=\"#/G4308 - προοράω - prooráō - pro-or-ah'-o/4308\">G4308</a>, <a href=\"#/G517 - ἀόρατος - aóratos - ah-or'-at-os/517\">G517</a>"}]}